<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="20600000t" end="56100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">大家知道数学史上最美丽的公式吗？</font></p>
<p begin="67700000t" end="91900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">e   +1=0</font></p>
<p begin="67700000t" end="91900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45"><font size="25">iπ</font></font></p>
<p begin="95300000t" end="116500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">也就是所谓的「欧拉恒等式」</font></p>
<p begin="127800000t" end="166600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">将自然对数的底e和圆周率π与虚数i</font></p>
<p begin="166600000t" end="196600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">再加上1和0这两个数融于一个公式中</font></p>
<p begin="196600000t" end="225000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这没有任何余赘仿佛浑然天成一般的公式</font></p>
<p begin="228300000t" end="286300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">或许是可以证明这世上有神存在的证据之一</font></p>
<p begin="287500000t" end="305900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}有趣的是，这里的美正体现在其恒等性上</font></p>
<p begin="296300000t" end="305900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}虽然美丽，但从这个角度考虑，却显得略有些可怕</font></p>
<p begin="305900000t" end="343000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">然而要让忍野扇  那个转校生来讲的话</font></p>
<p begin="343000000t" end="392600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">在欧拉恒等式的美这一点上  她或许也会说出如此沉重的话语</font></p>
<p begin="396400000t" end="407200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">就像这样</font></p>
<p begin="411400000t" end="448500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯  的确很美  阿良良木学长</font></p>
<p begin="451400000t" end="486500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">美丽得让人不禁晕过去</font></p>
<p begin="492300000t" end="528200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">其最美的一点就在于结果等于0</font></p>
<p begin="530700000t" end="561100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不过让我来说  既然结果等于0</font></p>
<p begin="561100000t" end="595300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">也就意味着没有去计算的必要了</font></p>
<p begin="598700000t" end="626600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">听了这一番话我如此想道</font></p>
<p begin="631200000t" end="649590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">忍野扇就是忍野扇</font></p>
<p begin="649590000t" end="670000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">一切多余的表述在她面前全是徒劳</font></p>
<p begin="677100000t" end="694200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">在她的面前一切为0</font></p>
<p begin="699200000t" end="718400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">就算她做出什么不符合她风格的行为</font></p>
<p begin="720100000t" end="737600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">最终都会变成她的风格</font></p>
<p begin="747200000t" end="775500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">于是这次便是一部关于数学的物语</font></p>
<p begin="782600000t" end="794700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">大家一起来学习吧</font></p>
<p begin="800100000t" end="833100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">说起数学  或许会给人一种死板的印象</font></p>
<p begin="833100000t" end="857300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那么我们就在此将其称之为算数好了</font></p>
<p begin="861400000t" end="891900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">甚至可以极端一点  将其称为关于数的故事</font></p>
<p begin="897300000t" end="929800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">因为这就是个由数量多少来决定的故事</font></p>
<p begin="933200000t" end="961100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">也就是多数决的故事</font></p>
<p begin="976100000t" end="986100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">多数决原则</font></p>
<p begin="994100000t" end="1027900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这也是能将错误变为真实的唯一途径</font></p>
<p begin="1034500000t" end="1063700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">并非追求幸福  而是追求合谋的</font></p>
<p begin="1063700000t" end="1079600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">如同堆积积木一般的方式</font></p>
<p begin="1083700000t" end="1116700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我们的不等式  我们的不当式</font></p>
<p begin="1116700000t" end="1120500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}不等式</font></p>
<p begin="1120500000t" end="1127100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}不当式</font></p>
<p begin="1128800000t" end="1169200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">真正愈义上由人类发明的事物或许就是如此</font></p>
<p begin="1173400000t" end="1214700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">而这也是人类史上最丑陋的公式</font></p>
<p begin="1369400000t" end="1401600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40"><font face="华文中宋" size="40">来吧  打开这扇门</font></p>
<p begin="1369400000t" end="1401600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="40">{\an8}さあ   扉を開けて</font></p>
<p begin="1401600000t" end="1438300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42"><font face="华文中宋" size="40">现在就开始冒险</font></p>
<p begin="1401600000t" end="1438300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="40">{\an8}冒険を今始めよう</font></p>
<p begin="1438300000t" end="1470000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44"><font face="华文中宋" size="40">来吧  我们一起寻找出</font></p>
<p begin="1438300000t" end="1470000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="40">{\an8}ねえ   正しい未来へ</font></p>
<p begin="1470000000t" end="1510400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46"><font face="华文中宋" size="40">导向正确未来的真实答案</font></p>
<p begin="1470000000t" end="1510400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="40">{\an8}続く答え见つけよう</font></p>
<p begin="1510800000t" end="1545000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48"><font face="华文中宋" size="40">这也想做  那也想做</font></p>
<p begin="1510800000t" end="1545000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="40">{\an8}あれもしたい   これもしたいって</font></p>
<p begin="1545500000t" end="1579700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50"><font face="华文中宋" size="40">一条贪欲的法则</font></p>
<p begin="1545500000t" end="1579700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="40">{\an8}欲張りの法則</font></p>
<p begin="1579700000t" end="1613400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52"><font face="华文中宋" size="40">这也不行  那也不行</font></p>
<p begin="1579700000t" end="1613400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="40">{\an8}あれもダメ   これもダメって</font></p>
<p begin="1613400000t" end="1647600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54"><font face="华文中宋" size="40">结果到处都是矛盾</font></p>
<p begin="1613400000t" end="1647600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="40">{\an8}結局矛盾だらけ</font></p>
<p begin="1648100000t" end="1712300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56"><font face="华文中宋" size="40">就在一些都完美齐备的瞬间</font></p>
<p begin="1648100000t" end="1712300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="40">{\an8}ぴったりと揃う   その瞬间に</font></p>
<p begin="1712700000t" end="1781100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58"><font face="华文中宋" size="40">完美齐备的一切在这瞬间也成为了虚假</font></p>
<p begin="1712700000t" end="1781100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="40">{\an8}ぴったりと揃う   嘘の瞬间</font></p>
<p begin="1781100000t" end="1813200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60"><font face="华文中宋" size="40">来吧  打开这扇门</font></p>
<p begin="1781100000t" end="1813200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="40">{\an8}さあ   扉を開けて</font></p>
<p begin="1813200000t" end="1849500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62"><font face="华文中宋" size="40">现在就开始冒险</font></p>
<p begin="1813200000t" end="1849500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="40">{\an8}冒険を今始めよう</font></p>
<p begin="1849900000t" end="1881200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64"><font face="华文中宋" size="40">来吧  我们一起寻找出</font></p>
<p begin="1849900000t" end="1881200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="40">{\an8}ねえ   正しい未来へ</font></p>
<p begin="1881600000t" end="1917900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66"><font face="华文中宋" size="40">导向正确未来的真实答案</font></p>
<p begin="1881600000t" end="1917900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="40">{\an8}続く答え見つけよう</font></p>
<p begin="1917900000t" end="1949600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68"><font face="华文中宋" size="40">就算不去直视</font></p>
<p begin="1917900000t" end="1949600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="40">{\an8}目を背けたままで</font></p>
<p begin="1950000000t" end="1987100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70"><font face="华文中宋" size="40">曾经的后悔依然不会消失</font></p>
<p begin="1950000000t" end="1987100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="40">{\an8}やり過ごした倒悔も</font></p>
<p begin="1987100000t" end="2018000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72"><font face="华文中宋" size="40">就算塞住耳朵</font></p>
<p begin="1987100000t" end="2018000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="40">{\an8}耳を塞りだまま</font></p>
<p begin="2018000000t" end="2059300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74"><font face="华文中宋" size="40">曾经的果实也依然存在</font></p>
<p begin="2018000000t" end="2059300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="40">{\an8}しまい込んだ過ちもね</font></p>
<p begin="2059700000t" end="2098900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76"><font face="华文中宋" size="40">请不要再走向那条错误的道路</font></p>
<p begin="2059700000t" end="2098900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="40">{\an8}もう二度と間違わないように</font></p>
<p begin="2132700000t" end="2159800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="32">{\an8}扇与方程式  其一</font></p>
<p begin="2175300000t" end="2213600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">如果有人有和初次见面的学妹在神秘的教室中</font></p>
<p begin="2215700000t" end="2231100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">处于封闭的二人世界</font></p>
<p begin="2233600000t" end="2267000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">并经过了超过一个小时时间的经验</font></p>
<p begin="2267000000t" end="2296600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那我一定会向他寻求一下建议</font></p>
<p begin="2308300000t" end="2329200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">没用啊  阿良良木学长</font></p>
<p begin="2332500000t" end="2372500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">啊  我刚才不是说阿良良木学长您没用</font></p>
<p begin="2375500000t" end="2395100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">而是说我尝试了不少方法</font></p>
<p begin="2396700000t" end="2433400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不论是大窗还是高窗全都纹丝不动的意思</font></p>
<p begin="2445900000t" end="2516800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不  我觉得这种状况下很难会误解成我这个人很没用吧</font></p>
<p begin="2526900000t" end="2541500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我这儿也没用啊</font></p>
<p begin="2547300000t" end="2570600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">也不像是上了锁</font></p>
<p begin="2570600000t" end="2620290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">好像是被胶水粘住了一样</font></p>
<p begin="2622800000t" end="2661600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯  就像刚才说过的一样  窗子纹丝不动</font></p>
<p begin="2665700000t" end="2712900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">说起上锁  上面的卡锁倒是可以动的</font></p>
<p begin="2723700000t" end="2754200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">然而关键的窗框却动不了</font></p>
<p begin="2756300000t" end="2809200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">没错  就像用胶水粘住了「一样的感觉」</font></p>
<p begin="2825100000t" end="2853000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">没办法  我们迎是等待外部救援吧</font></p>
<p begin="2853000000t" end="2900100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">小扇  幸好神原知道我们在这儿</font></p>
<p begin="2902600000t" end="2943900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这可不好说  这样一来就是等别人救了  阿良良木学长</font></p>
<p begin="2952700000t" end="3006500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">毕竟人只能自己救自己</font></p>
<p begin="3014000000t" end="3037800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">抱歉  这是我舅舅奉行的主义</font></p>
<p begin="3041500000t" end="3069500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">和我还有阿良良木学长没有任何关系</font></p>
<p begin="3082800000t" end="3112000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">先不说这些  阿良良木学长</font></p>
<p begin="3114900000t" end="3141600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">虽然依赖同伴也不是什么坏事</font></p>
<p begin="3144600000t" end="3208800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">然而我们还不能放弃尝试靠我们自己逃脱密室</font></p>
<p begin="3210900000t" end="3220000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">要说为什么的话…</font></p>
<p begin="3263400000t" end="3301800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">钟上的指针从我们进入教室的时候开始</font></p>
<p begin="3301800000t" end="3331800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">一分一秒也没有移动过</font></p>
<p begin="3336800000t" end="3380600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">应该也不是没电了吧</font></p>
<p begin="3398600000t" end="3422300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">故事的开端是从春假时</font></p>
<p begin="3424800000t" end="3467800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我被金发金眼的吸血鬼袭击之后又过了半年</font></p>
<p begin="3467800000t" end="3491600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">是十月下旬的某一天</font></p>
<p begin="3498200000t" end="3525400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">呀！阿良良木学长  我神原骏河来啦</font></p>
<p begin="3528300000t" end="3543300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你现在一个人吗？是一个人吧</font></p>
<p begin="3545800000t" end="3575800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我有个人要介绍给阿良良木学长认识</font></p>
<p begin="3597900000t" end="3612900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">可爱吧</font></p>
<p begin="3614600000t" end="3650500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那个女生是什么人？为什么要介绍给我？</font></p>
<p begin="3650500000t" end="3678800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">她有事找阿良良木学长商量</font></p>
<p begin="3681800000t" end="3702600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你就去和她见一面吧</font></p>
<p begin="3708500000t" end="3728900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">有什么事要和我商量？</font></p>
<p begin="3728900000t" end="3752200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我也不太清楚</font></p>
<p begin="3762300000t" end="3781000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不过似乎是和怪异有关</font></p>
<p begin="3781900000t" end="3786400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">呃？</font></p>
<p begin="3791500000t" end="3821900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯  她好像知道些什么内情</font></p>
<p begin="3824400000t" end="3869400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不仅知道我左手的  事连阿良良木学长血的事也知道</font></p>
<p begin="3874500000t" end="3894900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">据说是从舅舅那儿听来的</font></p>
<p begin="3899500000t" end="3909500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">舅舅？</font></p>
<p begin="3910700000t" end="3942000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">她是最近转学过来的一年级生</font></p>
<p begin="3949900000t" end="3985800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">令人吃惊的是  她好像是忍野先生的外甥女</font></p>
<p begin="3995800000t" end="4021700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">名字叫忍野扇</font></p>
<p begin="4056300000t" end="4070100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不对劲啊</font></p>
<p begin="4081300000t" end="4090900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不对劲…</font></p>
<p begin="4095500000t" end="4108400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不可思议</font></p>
<p begin="4115900000t" end="4124700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不可思议…</font></p>
<p begin="4126800000t" end="4145100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">也就是  很怪</font></p>
<p begin="4151800000t" end="4162200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">奇怪</font></p>
<p begin="4164300000t" end="4172200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">而又相异</font></p>
<p begin="4208100000t" end="4223100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">很奇怪啊</font></p>
<p begin="4265300000t" end="4294500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你在听我说话吗？阿良良木学长</font></p>
<p begin="4294500000t" end="4307400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">啊  那个…</font></p>
<p begin="4313200000t" end="4339100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你是说校舍或多了吗？</font></p>
<p begin="4342400000t" end="4387900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">从全校人数考虑  应该可以节约在一栋校舍之内</font></p>
<p begin="4393300000t" end="4405000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">完全不对</font></p>
<p begin="4409600000t" end="4425800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你怎么这么蠢啊？</font></p>
<p begin="4438800000t" end="4458800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我想说的是这里</font></p>
<p begin="4462100000t" end="4468800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">哪里？</font></p>
<p begin="4471300000t" end="4478000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这里</font></p>
<p begin="4482100000t" end="4496700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">格局很奇怪</font></p>
<p begin="4502600000t" end="4521800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">与其说奇怪不如说不自然</font></p>
<p begin="4525100000t" end="4553900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你看一下正上方和正下方的楼层</font></p>
<p begin="4559300000t" end="4577200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">上下都有一个房间对吧</font></p>
<p begin="4582200000t" end="4629800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">所以中间这里没有一个房间就显得很奇怪了</font></p>
<p begin="4638500000t" end="4651900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">奇怪？</font></p>
<p begin="4659000000t" end="4703600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">可是三层这里不也有一个房间吗？视听教室</font></p>
<p begin="4705300000t" end="4726100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这是示意图有误</font></p>
<p begin="4729100000t" end="4771600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">其实也不能说是有误  这里也是根据现实画出来的</font></p>
<p begin="4774100000t" end="4803700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">然而实际上视听教室并没有这么长</font></p>
<p begin="4811200000t" end="4857500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">和其他教室比起来长了有1.5倍</font></p>
<p begin="4876300000t" end="4915500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">哎？莫非您是在怀疑我吗？阿良良木学长</font></p>
<p begin="4918000000t" end="4950900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">太伤心了  居然被阿良良木学长怀疑</font></p>
<p begin="4952600000t" end="4996400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">话说你对我的感情还没好到被怀疑就受伤的地步吧</font></p>
<p begin="4998100000t" end="5023500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不不不  我可是相当崇拜您的</font></p>
<p begin="5025600000t" end="5054000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">崇拜像您这样简单就能上当受骗的蠢人</font></p>
<p begin="5074400000t" end="5124000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">如果是在推理小说中出现这样示意图和实际不符的情况</font></p>
<p begin="5124000000t" end="5157400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">大多数都预示着这里有一个隐藏房间</font></p>
<p begin="5163200000t" end="5176200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">但是如果…</font></p>
<p begin="5186200000t" end="5211590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这是某种怪异现象的话</font></p>
<p begin="5216590000t" end="5256700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我想我们还是应该在出现受害者之前调查一下</font></p>
<p begin="5382600000t" end="5408500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">哎？这个教室是怎么回事？</font></p>
<p begin="5411000000t" end="5464800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我在绘制示意图的时候可没有发现</font></p>
<p begin="5469800000t" end="5489800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">真是个谜啊</font></p>
<p begin="5491100000t" end="5514800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">总之我们先进去看看吧</font></p>
<p begin="5663700000t" end="5685800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">然后就发展成了如今的局面</font></p>
<p begin="5694600000t" end="5716300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你有什么想法吗？阿良良木学长</font></p>
<p begin="5720000000t" end="5748000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">什么想法？我自然也是一头雾水</font></p>
<p begin="5754200000t" end="5789300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不过小扇  如果这是某种怪异现象的话</font></p>
<p begin="5789300000t" end="5803900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那这又是什么怪异呢？</font></p>
<p begin="5807200000t" end="5833900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不知道  我和舅舅不一样</font></p>
<p begin="5833900000t" end="5862300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">对这种古老的知识一点也不了解</font></p>
<p begin="5866900000t" end="5898600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">只知道一些漫画电影里常见的怪异</font></p>
<p begin="5906900000t" end="5919800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不过阿良良木学长</font></p>
<p begin="5926500000t" end="5937800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">有一句话我还是可以明确说出来的</font></p>
<p begin="5946900000t" end="5982000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">「每个怪异都有着符合其自身存在的理由」</font></p>
<p begin="5998200000t" end="6009900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}也就是说，只要理清了它存在的理由，就可以从这儿出去了</font></p>
<p begin="6010300000t" end="6053700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">就算是这样  被关在教室里这件事本身又有什么理由呢？</font></p>
<p begin="6058300000t" end="6077100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">时钟不走也是一样</font></p>
<p begin="6081200000t" end="6110900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">关键不是在于时钟停止的时间吗？</font></p>
<p begin="6115400000t" end="6160100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">说不定就是这么回事  指着这么乱七八糟的时间肯定有问题</font></p>
<p begin="6166700000t" end="6195500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">下午六点就是学校放学的时间</font></p>
<p begin="6201800000t" end="6270200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">在学生必须回家的时间  这个被关在教室里的现象又有什么意义呢？</font></p>
<p begin="6280200000t" end="6302300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">明明是放学时间却不能回家</font></p>
<p begin="6320200000t" end="6344000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">是不是上课拖堂了啊？</font></p>
<p begin="6352300000t" end="6362400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">拖堂…</font></p>
<p begin="6387000000t" end="6420300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">阿良良木学长遇到过上课拖堂的情况吗？</font></p>
<p begin="6423700000t" end="6459500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">啊哈哈  我也算是脑袋比较聪明的</font></p>
<p begin="6462500000t" end="6485400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不过我倒没有什么印象</font></p>
<p begin="6487900000t" end="6501200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我也没什么印象</font></p>
<p begin="6504600000t" end="6525400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">哎？是嘛</font></p>
<p begin="6531300000t" end="6578800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">对于我来说  就算上课拖堂我也大多就直接翘掉了</font></p>
<p begin="6585900000t" end="6608800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不过去年还是前年来着</font></p>
<p begin="6611800000t" end="6630100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">好像是一年级的时候</font></p>
<p begin="6640500000t" end="6653500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">一年级的时候？</font></p>
<p begin="6679300000t" end="6695200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">怎么了？阿良良木学长</font></p>
<p begin="6695200000t" end="6711000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你的旗色不太好啊</font></p>
<p begin="6714000000t" end="6738100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不  我是说你的气色不太好</font></p>
<p begin="6739400000t" end="6779000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯  是吗？抱歉  我有点…头晕</font></p>
<p begin="6782800000t" end="6822000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">您用不着道歉的  完全不用道歉</font></p>
<p begin="6824900000t" end="6872400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">您一定是因为在靠不住的学妹面前逞强而感到疲惫了吧</font></p>
<p begin="6880400000t" end="6902900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">快在那边的椅子上坐一会儿吧</font></p>
<p begin="7022200000t" end="7040500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你为什么要坐在那儿呢？</font></p>
<p begin="7043500000t" end="7073900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯？怎么了？为什么要这么问？</font></p>
<p begin="7077700000t" end="7099300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不是小扇你让我坐下的吗？</font></p>
<p begin="7101000000t" end="7144800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不不不  我是问教室里有这么多椅子</font></p>
<p begin="7144800000t" end="7168600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">您为什么非要坐在那个位置？</font></p>
<p begin="7194900000t" end="7204400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">凭感觉</font></p>
<p begin="7208200000t" end="7217800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">凭感觉</font></p>
<p begin="7219900000t" end="7255700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那个位子很方便吗？还是说椅子很舒服？</font></p>
<p begin="7257800000t" end="7303300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不  要说舒服的话  大部分椅子应该都差不多吧</font></p>
<p begin="7310800000t" end="7324100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">只是有些…</font></p>
<p begin="7325800000t" end="7339200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">只是有些？</font></p>
<p begin="7347500000t" end="7362500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">有种坐习惯了的…</font></p>
<p begin="7374600000t" end="7384600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">感觉</font></p>
<p begin="7403400000t" end="7415100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">真的吗？</font></p>
<p begin="7417600000t" end="7441300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">什么？怎么了？小扇</font></p>
<p begin="7447600000t" end="7475500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">没什么  我只是在分析可能性而已</font></p>
<p begin="7481800000t" end="7495200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">作为可能性的一种</font></p>
<p begin="7496800000t" end="7537700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">或许阿良良木学长过去坐过这把椅子</font></p>
<p begin="7537700000t" end="7587300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">所以在要休息的时候就自然而然地选择了这个位子</font></p>
<p begin="7591100000t" end="7616500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不会吧  这也太离谱了</font></p>
<p begin="7621500000t" end="7659500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">刚才我还不知道在这儿有个教室呢</font></p>
<p begin="7664900000t" end="7718300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我刚来这里调查的时候也没发现这个教室</font></p>
<p begin="7722000000t" end="7765800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">然而和阿良良木学长一起过来的时候  这个教室就凭空出现了</font></p>
<p begin="7769600000t" end="7826700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那么认为这个教室和阿良良木学长有什么关系就是很自然的事情了</font></p>
<p begin="7856300000t" end="7882200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">而且你不是也说过了吗？阿良良木学长</font></p>
<p begin="7883900000t" end="7921400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">「总觉得从窗子看到的风景似乎在哪儿见过」</font></p>
<p begin="7923900000t" end="7942300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">哎？我说过那种话吗？</font></p>
<p begin="7944400000t" end="7953900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">当然说过</font></p>
<p begin="7955600000t" end="7971000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">就在刚进入教室的时候</font></p>
<p begin="7971000000t" end="7971000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">在我们还没发现被关住的时候</font></p>
<p begin="8000700000t" end="8017800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">可我却不记得了</font></p>
<p begin="8017800000t" end="8059000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不过  她既然能如此断言  那应该是说过吧</font></p>
<p begin="8072800000t" end="8094900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">似乎  怎么说呢…</font></p>
<p begin="8097800000t" end="8118700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">感觉记忆被激活了</font></p>
<p begin="8407300000t" end="8432800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">哎呀哎呀？怎么了？阿良良木学长</font></p>
<p begin="8435700000t" end="8464500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不像是想起了什么的样子啊</font></p>
<p begin="8466500000t" end="8496600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">莫非我说了什么煞风景的话</font></p>
<p begin="8499500000t" end="8532000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">让您想起了什么不愿想起的回忆？</font></p>
<p begin="8539500000t" end="8562500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不  不是这样</font></p>
<p begin="8565000000t" end="8581200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我什么也没想起来</font></p>
<p begin="8584600000t" end="8613800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">没错  我什么也没想起来</font></p>
<p begin="8618800000t" end="8648800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">因为  我从来就没有忘记</font></p>
<p begin="8661700000t" end="8693000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那件事我是不可能忘记的</font></p>
<p begin="8684700000t" end="8696800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}一年三班  阿良良木历</font></p>
<p begin="8713900000t" end="8751000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">哎呀哎呀？刚才课本上写的不是阿良良木么？</font></p>
<p begin="8753900000t" end="8774800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle253"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">好奇怪  不可思议</font></p>
<p begin="8774800000t" end="8816900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle254"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">阿良良木学长的课本为什么会在这个教室里？</font></p>
<p begin="8826900000t" end="8862400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle255"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">小扇  你是不是知道什么？</font></p>
<p begin="8866100000t" end="8885700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle256"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我什么都不知道</font></p>
<p begin="8889900000t" end="8906600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle257"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">是你自己知道</font></p>
<p begin="8972900000t" end="9016700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle258"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">小扇  这儿有没有什么能表示日期的东西？</font></p>
<p begin="9019600000t" end="9031700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle259"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">日期是吗？</font></p>
<p begin="9033400000t" end="9058400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯  今天…不</font></p>
<p begin="9062100000t" end="9089700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这个教室里究竟是几月几号？</font></p>
<p begin="9092600000t" end="9123000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">黑板上不是都写着么？</font></p>
<p begin="9127200000t" end="9146000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle263"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">您仔细看一看啊  瞧</font></p>
<p begin="9166800000t" end="9197300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle264"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">哎哟  今天是七月十五日啊</font></p>
<p begin="9215200000t" end="9237700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这样考虑应该没错了吧</font></p>
<p begin="9244000000t" end="9295300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">七月十五日周四下午六点左右  在这教室里发生了什么事情</font></p>
<p begin="9299500000t" end="9328200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这件事情导致某个人难以释怀</font></p>
<p begin="9330700000t" end="9377400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">一定是这种遗憾导致了某种怪异的形成</font></p>
<p begin="9414200000t" end="9450900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这个教室  校舍面向体育馆的五层</font></p>
<p begin="9454600000t" end="9476300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle270"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这一层最中间的一年三班</font></p>
<p begin="9478000000t" end="9505900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle271"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">在七月十五日放学后召开了一场班会</font></p>
<p begin="9511300000t" end="9530900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这场班会也可以称为一次审判</font></p>
<p begin="9538400000t" end="9572600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">围绕着某件事  我们互相指控</font></p>
<p begin="9579700000t" end="9641000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">而我  一年三班的阿良良木历正是处于审判的中心</font></p>
<p begin="9649000000t" end="9674400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">没错  就是从那一天开始</font></p>
<p begin="9676100000t" end="9695300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我第一次说出了那样的话</font></p>
<p begin="9698600000t" end="9752000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">「我不需要朋友  朋友只会让人际强度下降」</font></p>
<p begin="9767800000t" end="9791200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这可是阿良良木学长的口头禅吧</font></p>
<p begin="9793700000t" end="9841200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">虽然在和羽川翼学姐接触之后就再也没说过</font></p>
<p begin="9846300000t" end="9888800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">根据不同的邂逅  人也是会变的嘛</font></p>
<p begin="9894600000t" end="9917600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那我就出于好奇心地问一下吧</font></p>
<p begin="9921700000t" end="9954300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">在这个教室中  阿良良木学长是怎样改变的？</font></p>
<p begin="9959300000t" end="9997700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">一年三班的同学是怎样改变了你？</font></p>
<p begin="10003500000t" end="10020200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">改变了我？</font></p>
<p begin="10023500000t" end="10074000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">听说您中学和高中的性格差别很大啊</font></p>
<p begin="10078100000t" end="10118200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">莫非原因就出在这个教室里吗？</font></p>
<p begin="10139000000t" end="10162800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">究竟发生了什么事？阿良良木学长</font></p>
<p begin="10168700000t" end="10200800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">在这个教室  在那一天  那个时间</font></p>
<p begin="10212400000t" end="10238300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle289"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">快说出来吧  阿良良木学长</font></p>
<p begin="10243690000t" end="10257100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle290"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">阿良良木历</font></p>
<p begin="10263800000t" end="10280400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">说出来就轻松多了</font></p>
<p begin="10282500000t" end="10319200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45"><font size="36">故事</font></font></p>
<p begin="10282500000t" end="10319200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不论是多么痛苦的回忆  只要说出来就只不过是一个物语</font></p>
<p begin="10325890000t" end="10337600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">物语…</font></p>
<p begin="10325890000t" end="10337600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45"><font size="36">故事</font></font></p>
<p begin="10339700000t" end="10363000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">没关系  我会认真听的</font></p>
<p begin="10369300000t" end="10403900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle297"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">别看我这个样子  我可是个很好的倾诉对象</font></p>
<p begin="10440990000t" end="10450990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle298"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">出不去了</font></p>
<p begin="10454800000t" end="10461400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle299"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">什么？</font></p>
<p begin="10467700000t" end="10477700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle300"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我们出不去了</font></p>
<p begin="10481900000t" end="10519400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle301"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">如果不确定出一个犯人  我们就不准从教室里出去</font></p>
<p begin="10529900000t" end="10564900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle302"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我们所做的事  我们强加在自己身上的</font></p>
<p begin="10567800000t" end="10582800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">就是这样的班会</font></p>
<p begin="10592800000t" end="10610800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">虽然难以置信</font></p>
<p begin="10614900000t" end="10647500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle305"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">在这次班会中  我担任着议长的职务</font></p>
<p begin="10682900000t" end="10695400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle306"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}两年前</font></p>
<p begin="10776300000t" end="10800500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle307"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">她的名字是老仓育</font></p>
<p begin="10803000000t" end="10851400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">虽然她希望我们叫她「欧拉」  但大家都叫她「How much」</font></p>
<p begin="10853500000t" end="10862700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle309"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}How much</font></p>
<p begin="10867300000t" end="10891500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle310"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">虽然是个从姓氏演变而来的绰号</font></p>
<p begin="10894400000t" end="10944000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle311"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">但对于总是衡量他人价值的她来说却也出乎意料地合适</font></p>
<p begin="10948600000t" end="10960300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle312"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}老仓育</font></p>
<p begin="10982000000t" end="10991100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle313"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">老仓班长</font></p>
<p begin="10998700000t" end="11017800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle314"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">是你叫我？</font></p>
<p begin="11026600000t" end="11062900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle315"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">快点进来  大家都在等你呢</font></p>
<p begin="11137500000t" end="11198900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle316"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">教室中  一年三班的成员一个不少  全员在场</font></p>
<p begin="11208900000t" end="11247700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle317"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">啊  全员啊  也就是完整的阵容</font></p>
<p begin="11267300000t" end="11319400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle318"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">虽然现在是个无人的教室  看来当时每个座位都坐着人</font></p>
<p begin="11322300000t" end="11366900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle319"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">原来如此原来如此  真是光阴似箭  十年一日啊</font></p>
<p begin="11369400000t" end="11391500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle320"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}十年一日</font></p>
<p begin="11370300000t" end="11402000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle321"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">啊  不…不是十年  而是两年</font></p>
<p begin="11391500000t" end="11404500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle322"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}两年一日</font></p>
<p begin="11408600000t" end="11445800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle323"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">如果说起细节的话  老仓她是站在讲桌那儿的</font></p>
<p begin="11448700000t" end="11467000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle324"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">讲桌上面？</font></p>
<p begin="11468700000t" end="11493300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle325"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">老仓可不是那么有个性的班长</font></p>
<p begin="11498300000t" end="11533400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle326"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这些先姑且不论  她站在讲桌后宣布道</font></p>
<p begin="11542100000t" end="11573800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle327"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">「现在开始举行临时班会」</font></p>
<p begin="11593000000t" end="11662200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle328"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">真不可思议  阿良良木学长之前对这个班会完全不知情吧</font></p>
<p begin="11665200000t" end="11696800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle329"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那只是通知有所遗漏而已</font></p>
<p begin="11699800000t" end="11734000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle330"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那一天  全班同学都被某种联络网…</font></p>
<p begin="11736500000t" end="11778200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle331"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">比如纸条  邮件等手段通知</font></p>
<p begin="11781900000t" end="11810700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle332"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">然而任何手段都没有通知到我</font></p>
<p begin="11819500000t" end="11871600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle333"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">哎？难道说…这就是现在所说的被排挤的家伙吧</font></p>
<p begin="11872400000t" end="11886200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle334"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">稍微有些误会</font></p>
<p begin="11886200000t" end="11895400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle335"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}虽然不是完全误会</font></p>
<p begin="11897900000t" end="11959200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle336"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">小扇  我想说的是一部没有朋友的人变成不需要朋友的人的物语</font></p>
<p begin="11965500000t" end="11991300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle337"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那我就重整姿势  再听您继续讲下去好了</font></p>
<p begin="11994200000t" end="12016800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle338"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">听您讲那场临时班会的故事</font></p>
<p begin="12020500000t" end="12043400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle339"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">以及班会今日的议题</font></p>
<p begin="12065100000t" end="12089700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle340"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">首先  老仓开门见山地这样说道</font></p>
<p begin="12093100000t" end="12114800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle341"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">今天的议题是寻找犯人</font></p>
<p begin="12118100000t" end="12156500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle342"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">在确定出犯人  亦或是犯人自己承认之前</font></p>
<p begin="12159800000t" end="12192300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle343"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">谁也不许离开这间教室  就是这样</font></p>
<p begin="12239100000t" end="12269900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle344"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我向战场原绯多木的座位看过去</font></p>
<p begin="12275800000t" end="12291200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle345"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">她是个十分病弱的少女</font></p>
<p begin="12293700000t" end="12319100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle346"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">给人一种学期一半的时间都在请假的印象</font></p>
<p begin="12327100000t" end="12377900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle347"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">就连她都出席了这次班会  看来事态还真的是很严重</font></p>
<p begin="12391300000t" end="12441800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle348"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">寻找犯人  还真是不得了  到底发生了什么事？</font></p>
<p begin="12447200000t" end="12472200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle349"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">或许是期末考试前几天的事情</font></p>
<p begin="12475500000t" end="12514300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle350"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">班里募集了志愿者并举行了一场数学学习会</font></p>
<p begin="12514300000t" end="12549400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle351"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="33">{\an8}写给一年三班全体同学<br />一年三班班长  老仓育<br />学习会的通知<br />前期期末考试即将来临，部分有志者准备举办一场学习会。<br />希望可以为大家的学习带来一些帮助。请大家积极参加。<br />1.地点：一年三班  教室<br />2.时间：七月七日（周三）15:00~18:00<br />3.内容：数学ⅢC<br />有意参加者请联系老仓</font></p>
<p begin="12519800000t" end="12547700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle352"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">老仓似乎也参加了</font></p>
<p begin="12550600000t" end="12569000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle353"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">哎？学习会？</font></p>
<p begin="12571500000t" end="12663600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle354"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">然而考试之后  参加学习会的人和没参加的人之间出现了20分的分差</font></p>
<p begin="12669900000t" end="12697400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle355"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">「这是某种意义的作弊」</font></p>
<p begin="12697400000t" end="12718300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle356"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">老仓是这样主张的</font></p>
<p begin="12723300000t" end="12760800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle357"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">应该是某个人从办公室拿到了考试题目</font></p>
<p begin="12762500000t" end="12799600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle358"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">并在学习会上公布了出来  使其自然流出</font></p>
<p begin="12803800000t" end="12850100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle359"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">参加学习会的学生就是这样提高了成绩</font></p>
<p begin="12861300000t" end="12914300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle360"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">如果有人给神圣的学习会和不可侵犯的期末考试带来了污点</font></p>
<p begin="12916000000t" end="12935200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle361"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这绝对是不可饶恕的行为</font></p>
<p begin="12940200000t" end="12984800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle362"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">没参加学习会的同学也不要以为事情和自己无关</font></p>
<p begin="12989000000t" end="13024400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle363"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这是我们一年三班全体的问题</font></p>
<p begin="13028200000t" end="13040300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle364"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我重复一遍</font></p>
<p begin="13082800000t" end="13117400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle365"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">在确定出犯人  亦或是犯人自己承认之前</font></p>
<p begin="13122000000t" end="13160000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle366"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">谁也不许离开这间教室  就是这样</font></p>
<p begin="13166200000t" end="13238000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle367"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">嗯？这么说来  是老仓学姐后来把议长的位置让给了阿良良木学长？</font></p>
<p begin="13243000000t" end="13283900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle368"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">阿良良木学长您刚才说是您担任了议长的职务对吧</font></p>
<p begin="13285900000t" end="13315100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle369"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">啊  没有错  后来更换了议长</font></p>
<p begin="13319700000t" end="13346000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle370"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那阿良良木学长是如何被提名的呢？</font></p>
<p begin="13351400000t" end="13389400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle371"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">让参加了学习会的人主持会议显然不太好</font></p>
<p begin="13393100000t" end="13423600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle372"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">虽然这样  但这也不是除了他们之外的什么人都可以胜任的</font></p>
<p begin="13428600000t" end="13461100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle373"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">毕竟议题的核心是数学考试</font></p>
<p begin="13466100000t" end="13494100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle374"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不可避免地会涉及到验证考试题目的问题</font></p>
<p begin="13499900000t" end="13550800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle375"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">因此也不能让数学成绩不好的人主持</font></p>
<p begin="13555400000t" end="13578700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle376"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">啊  有道理</font></p>
<p begin="13585800000t" end="13660500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle377"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不过在学习会缺席  也就是没有参加的学生成绩相对而言低了20多分</font></p>
<p begin="13663400000t" end="13727600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle378"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">在没参加的学生中真有成绩不亚于参加了学习会的学生的人吗？</font></p>
<p begin="13731800000t" end="13746400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle379"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">有的</font></p>
<p begin="13748900000t" end="13796000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle380"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">然而比所有参加了学习会的学生成绩都好的人</font></p>
<p begin="13799800000t" end="13813100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle381"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">就只有我一个</font></p>
<p begin="13814400000t" end="13819800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle382"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">哎？</font></p>
<p begin="13825200000t" end="13852300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle383"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这就是我之所以被选为议长的原因</font></p>
<p begin="13872400000t" end="13902000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle384"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">100分  100分满分中得了100分</font></p>
<p begin="13907800000t" end="13942000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle385"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这就是我数学期末考试的成绩</font></p>
<p begin="13947400000t" end="13973300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle386"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那我们就快点进行吧</font></p>
<p begin="13977900000t" end="13987100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle387"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">阿良良木同学</font></p>
<p begin="14012900000t" end="14030400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle388"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我想大家也看出来了</font></p>
<p begin="14032500000t" end="14085100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle389"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">老仓班长对我带有病态般厌恶的原因正是我擅长数学</font></p>
<p begin="14090900000t" end="14148900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle390"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">大家不愿叫她「欧拉」也是因为我的数学成绩比她好</font></p>
<p begin="14148900000t" end="14168100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle391"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">她对此深信不疑</font></p>
<p begin="14182700000t" end="14231000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle392"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">那么  请参加了学习会的同学举手</font></p>
<p begin="14245200000t" end="14259800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle393"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">结果非常清楚</font></p>
<p begin="14264400000t" end="14293600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle394"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">参加了学习会的学生共有19人</font></p>
<p begin="14319900000t" end="14363700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle395"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">也就是说犯人就锁定在这19人之中了</font></p>
<p begin="14366200000t" end="14381200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle396"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">真让人兴奋</font></p>
<p begin="14383700000t" end="14421700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle397"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不  说这种话还是有些不合适  要受禁闭处分的</font></p>
<p begin="14437100000t" end="14459600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle398"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">我事先说明  小扇</font></p>
<p begin="14465000000t" end="14494600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle399"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这次班会是不会找出犯人的</font></p>
<p begin="14505500000t" end="14526800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle400"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">气氛只是越来越险恶</font></p>
<p begin="14526800000t" end="14561000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle401"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">情况也变得越来越复杂  最终不了了之</font></p>
<p begin="14562600000t" end="14568900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle402"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">然后…</font></p>
<p begin="14584700000t" end="14643100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle403"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">对了  我们可以找出离开这间教室的方法了  阿良良木学长</font></p>
<p begin="14654000000t" end="14721500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle404"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">也就是说只要我们解决了两年前不了了之的事件就能出去了</font></p>
<p begin="14734500000t" end="14746100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle405"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这是什么意思？</font></p>
<p begin="14753200000t" end="14789100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle406"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">「在确定出犯人之前  谁也不许离开教室」</font></p>
<p begin="14789100000t" end="14807000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle407"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">老仓学姐不就是这么说的吗？</font></p>
<p begin="14811600000t" end="14870000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle408"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">反过来说  只要我们找出了事件的犯人就可以离开这里</font></p>
<p begin="14870000000t" end="14882100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle409"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">不就是这么回事吗？</font></p>
<p begin="14898400000t" end="14971400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle410"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">当时一年三班同学们心中的遗憾就这样在学校形成了隙间</font></p>
<p begin="14975500000t" end="15000600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle411"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">换句话说就是班会的幽灵</font></p>
<p begin="15003900000t" end="15018900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle412"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">班会的幽灵…</font></p>
<p begin="15021800000t" end="15061000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle413"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">你是说我就是被这种不明所以的东西因禁在这里吗？</font></p>
<p begin="15069000000t" end="15080600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle414"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">可为什么是我…</font></p>
<p begin="15083600000t" end="15132800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle415"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">看来  最介意这件事的应该就是阿良良木学长你了</font></p>
<p begin="15135700000t" end="15150300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle416"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">说不定就是这样</font></p>
<p begin="15157400000t" end="15190800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle417"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">因为阿良良木学长的人生在那一天完全变了样子</font></p>
<p begin="15202000000t" end="15212000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle418"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">完全变了样子</font></p>
<p begin="15214900000t" end="15254600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle419"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">从那一天开始  你就刻意不去考虑这件事</font></p>
<p begin="15254600000t" end="15266700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle420"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">忌讳这件事</font></p>
<p begin="15266700000t" end="15310500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle421"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">虽然从来没有忘记  但也从来没有考虑过</font></p>
<p begin="15317100000t" end="15350900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle422"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">这一天终于来了  直面过去的一天</font></p>
<p begin="15360500000t" end="15381800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle423"><font face="方正准圆_GBK" size="45">也是解开谜题的一天</font></p>
<p begin="15425100000t" end="15484300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle424"><font face="华文中宋" size="39" color="#f6d440">耳畔又传来你的笑声</font></p>
<p begin="15425100000t" end="15484300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle425"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}横で君の笑い声が聞こえる</font></p>
<p begin="15484700000t" end="15545200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle426"><font face="华文中宋" size="39" color="#f6d440">那本应该永远伴我身边的声音</font></p>
<p begin="15484700000t" end="15545200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle427"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}ずっと隣にいたはずの声</font></p>
<p begin="15666600000t" end="15749100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle428"><font face="华文中宋" size="39" color="#f6d440">在教室窗子上呼气的水雾中写下的名字</font></p>
<p begin="15666600000t" end="15749100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle429"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}教室の窓に息を吐いて描いた名前</font></p>
<p begin="15749100000t" end="15779600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle430"><font face="华文中宋" size="39" color="#f6d440">我慌忙地用袖子将它檫去</font></p>
<p begin="15749100000t" end="15779600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle431"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}もぅ慌てて袖で消した</font></p>
<p begin="15779600000t" end="15846700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle432"><font face="华文中宋" size="39" color="#f6d440">那是因为走廊中传来了你的声音</font></p>
<p begin="15779600000t" end="15846700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle433"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}廊下から君の声がしたから</font></p>
<p begin="15846700000t" end="15918900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle434"><font face="华文中宋" size="39" color="#f6d440">我假装毫不在意  早早地回了家</font></p>
<p begin="15846700000t" end="15918900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle435"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}心誤魔化すように早足で帰った</font></p>
<p begin="15918900000t" end="16002300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle436"><font face="华文中宋" size="39" color="#f6d440">不知从什么时候起我无法和你说话</font></p>
<p begin="15918900000t" end="16002300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle437"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}何時からか私は君と話せなくなった</font></p>
<p begin="16003100000t" end="16062400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle438"><font face="华文中宋" size="39" color="#f6d440">耳畔又传来你的笑声</font></p>
<p begin="16003100000t" end="16062400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle439"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}横で君の笑い声が聞こえる</font></p>
<p begin="16062800000t" end="16119100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle440"><font face="华文中宋" size="39" color="#f6d440">那本应该永远伴我身边的声音</font></p>
<p begin="16062800000t" end="16119100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle441"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}ずっと隣にいたはずの声</font></p>
<p begin="16119100000t" end="16175400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle442"><font face="华文中宋" size="39" color="#f6d440">无须说出任何话语就可以注意到自己的人比什么都重要</font></p>
<p begin="16119100000t" end="16175400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle443"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}何も言わなくたって すぐ気付いてくれた人</font></p>
<p begin="16175800000t" end="16245100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle444"><font face="华文中宋" size="39" color="#f6d440">即时此刻注意到这一点  然而我们已经无法再面对</font></p>
<p begin="16175800000t" end="16245100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle445"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}何より大切と気付いても もう目も合わない</font></p>
